#2048 Specification

State Item         | CSS Selector
-------------------|------------------------------------
Game Score         | .score-container
Best (High) Score  | .best-container
Tiles              | .tile
  score 2048       | .tile.tile-2048
  score 2048       | .tile .tile-inner{2048}
  position (2,3)   | .tile.tile-position-2-3
Game Over          | .game-message.game-over{Game over!}
Game Won           | .game-message.geme-won{You won!}
